name: CongCong
description: Cong Cong is one of the mascots of the 19th Asian Games in 2022. It represents the world heritage Liangzhu ancient city site with the shape of robot. Its name comes from the representative cultural relic jade Cong unearthed from Liangzhu ancient city site. It shows the indomitable entrepreneurial spirit and encourages people to stimulate their vitality,
